{"tid":2088392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍機連續10日飛過台空域","createTime":"2020-07-01T06:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T06:41:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bce45f9e9be28456a00d22e9390e587350b60ea7","tid":2088392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200701/WWANTZVO52PG2KUFXSCZJ543AY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200701%2FWWANTZVO52PG2KUFXSCZJ543AY%2F&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=26070cba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200701%2FWWANTZVO52PG2KUFXSCZJ543AY%2F&h=f485c248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200701/WWANTZVO52PG2KUFXSCZJ543AY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美軍機連續10日飛過台空域<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VU-yZbYqdTywfeaknDqGZ25ewpE=/703x535/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VKJ2TDVUVMCHEHATPM2VOIQLNM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVU-yZbYqdTywfeaknDqGZ25ewpE%3D%2F703x535%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVKJ2TDVUVMCHEHATPM2VOIQLNM.gif&h=f37bacc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸通過「港版國安法」敏感時刻，美軍一架P-8A反潛機（圖）由日本美軍厚木基地出發，通過台灣海峽後，前往南海執行任務，台軍方強調對周遭海空域全程監控，這是美軍機連續10天出現在台灣周邊空域。同時，台灣海軍潛艇據指於今日進行魚雷實彈射擊，這將是13年來海軍再次試射魚雷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台軍13年來首試射魚雷<br />\n<br />\n北京大學海洋研究院成立的「南海戰略態勢感知計劃」昨在Twitter發文，美軍一架P-8A反潛機從駐日美軍厚木基地起飛，前往南海執行任務，根據航迹圖，航路通過台灣海峽，一度距離中國海岸基準線不到45海里。而在前日，美軍五架偵察機、運輸機和空中加油機分別飛經巴士海峽前往南海一帶。台灣國防部不評論事件，強調台軍對於周邊海空域狀況都充份掌握，民眾可放心。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，台灣「國軍漢光36號」將在本<br />\n...............................<br />\n範圍幾乎涵蓋三沙市在內的西沙群島所有島嶼。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"469ba693e73997aec145dedae6ea6999ab6fdd14","tid":2088392,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"有閪用咩"},{"pid":"90e7f174112175cdc613463684bfce104830114b","tid":2088392,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"降落埋就最好"},{"pid":"6fccc973f5a0ba8e0f40e32b4d770f9db6f5e769","tid":2088392,"uid":357717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"通常呢d po 連登仔反應<br />\n美國飛南海：美國好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共飛台海：垃圾，打未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}